		<gesture>idle</gesture>
	</step>
	<step>
		<name>R1_LocatingStartPoint</name>
		<text>Your hunt starts at the pedestrian gate entrance to the Main Yard by the Janitor's Lodge. First, let's get there.</text>
		<gesture></gesture>
	</step>	
	<step>
		<name>R1_C1</name>
		<text>From the pedestrian gate entrance to the Main Yard by the Janitor's Lodge, turn west and pace 50 metres along the footpath on the north side of Henderson Row.</text>
