			<gesture></gesture>
		</question>	
	</step>
	<step>
		<name>R1_C2</name>
		<text>Carry on walking in the same direction and cross at the pedestrian crossing opposite Stockbridge Primary School. Wait for the Green Man before crossing. Cross over, turn left and then turn right onto Clarence Street.</text>		
